title: Senator Ron Johnson Is Re-elected in Wisconsin
description: Senator Ron Johnson, a Republican and one of the foremost spreaders of misinformation, won a third term, turning back a challenge from Lt. Gov. Mandela Barnes.
dc:creator: Reid J. Epstein
media:credit: Tim Gruber for The New York Times
media:description: Senator Ron Johnson of Wisconsin addressing supporters at his election night party in Neenah, Wis., on Wednesday.
